<p class="h1">APOCALYPSE*</p>
<p class="fl">Term meaning a “revelation” or a “disclosure.” The books of Daniel and Revelation are the two apocalypses in the Bible. <span class="ital">See</span> <a href="?item=Apocalyptic_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Apocalyptic</a>; <a href="?item=DanielBookof_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Daniel, Book of</a>; <a href="?item=RevelationBookof_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Revelation, Book of</a>.</p>
